rmarkettest/\" title=\"Resident Labour Market Test\">resident labour market test</a> for Tier 2 general workers </li>\n  <li>keep records of your employee</li>\n  <li>report changes in your employee&rsquo;s working status to the UK Border Agency (<abbr title=\"UK Border Agency\">UKBA</abbr>), eg if they stop showing up for work or they resign  </li>\n  <li>follow immigration laws</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If a sponsor doesn&rsquo;t follow these duties, their licence can be downgraded (from A to B status), suspended or taken away.</p>\n\n<p>Employers must give their employee a certificate of sponsorship so they can apply for a visa or extension of their stay. </p>\n\n<h2>Reporting</h2>\n\n<p>If a sponsored employee thinks that their employer has given false information or isn&rsquo;t carrying out their duties, they can get in touch with the Sponsor Licensing Unit.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Sponsor Licensing Unit - Intelligence Unit</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#119;&#111;&#114;&#107;&#097;&#098;&#117;&#115;&#101;&#064;&#104;&#111;&#109;&#101;&#111;&#102;&#102;&#105;&#099;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#119;&#111;&#114;&#107;&#097;&#098;&#117;&#115;&#101;&#064;&#104;&#111;&#109;&#101;&#111;&#102;&#102;&#105;&#099;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01142793480</p>\n</div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/uk-visa-sponsorship-employers/certificate-of-sponsorship","slug":"certificate-of-sponsorship","order":4,"title":"Certificate of sponsorship","body":"<p>The certificate is a virtual document with a unique reference number that lets employees apply for a visa or extension of their stay.  </p>\n\n<p>You must pay for each certificate of sponsorship you give but don’t get a refund if your employee does not use it.</p>\n\n<h2>Deadline to apply</h2>\n\n<p>Once a certificate of sponsorship is assigned to someone, they have 3 months to us